under pressure stem:[p] (<<t4-14.1>>) expressed by:

stem:[kappa= -1/V (\"d\"V)/(\"d\"p)]
"""@en ;
  skos:note """Conditions should be specified (e.g. isentropic or isothermal process).

See also <<iso80000-5>>.
"""@en ;
